dct_alternative_sm: Rand McNally & Co.'s New Indexed Atlas of the World
dct_description_sm: North is oriented towards top right corner of the map. Title at head of map: Rand McNally & Co.'s Detroit. Includes two copyright dates, 1895 and 1898. Includes index on verso, "Rand, McNally & Co.'s Michigan" includes county seats and location of money order P.O. Inset: Detroit and Vicinity, includes Grosse Isle. Page no. 229-232. 1 map: col.; 52 x 69 cm
